{"article_id":"nQpatroA9eSPomSy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democratic presidential candidate Joe Biden speaks about responses to the coronavirus pandemic at an event in Wilmington , Del. , March 12 , 2020 .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"( Carlos Barria/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"New York Times executive editor Dean Baquet said on Monday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that the paper made a controversial change to its report on the sexual-assault allegation against presumptive Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after his campaign complained about the wording .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"In an interview with Times media columnist Ben Smith , Baquet said","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"the Biden campaign took issue with some of the phrasing in the paper ' s report on former Senate staffer Tara Reade ' s allegation","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that Biden sexually assaulted her in 1993 .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"\" No other allegation about sexual assault surfaced in the course of reporting ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"nor did any former Biden staff members corroborate any details of Ms. Reade ' s allegation , \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"the report read .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" The Times found no pattern of sexual misconduct by Mr. Biden , beyond the hugs , kisses and touching","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"women previously said","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"made them uncomfortable . \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"The Times subsequently deleted the second half of that sentence ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"eliminating the description of Biden ' s conduct","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to which women have previously objected .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" I want to ask about some edits","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that were made after publication ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"the deletion of the second half of the sentence , \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Smith asked Baquet .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" Why did you do that ? \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" Even though a lot of us ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"including me ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"had looked at it","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"before the story went into the paper ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that the campaign thought","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"that the phrasing was awkward","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and made it look like there were other instances","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"in which he had been accused of sexual misconduct ,","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"and that ' s not what the sentence was intended to say , \"","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Baquet answered .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" We didn ' t think","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"it was a factual mistake , \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Baquet said .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"\" I thought","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"it was an awkward phrasing issue","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that could be read different ways","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and that it wasn ' t something factual","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"we were correcting .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"So , I didn ' t think","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that was necessary . \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"The Times did not add a correction or an editor ' s note to the report","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"after it was changed .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"The paper also deleted a tweet","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"relating to the report","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"and explained ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"\" We ' ve deleted a tweet in this thread","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that had some imprecise language","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that has been changed in the story . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Reade went public with graphic details about her claim on March 25 ,","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"and the Times report was published over two weeks later on Easter Sunday .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"\" I thought","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that what The New York Times could offer","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and should try to offer","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"was the reporting","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"to help people understand what to make of a fairly serious allegation against a guy","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"who had been a vice president of the United States","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and was knocking on the door","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"of being his party ' s nominee , \"","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"Baquet said ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"explaining","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"why the Times waited to report on the accusation .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"\" Look , I get the argument .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Just do a short , straightforward news story .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"But , I ' m not sure","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that doing this sort of straightforward news story would have helped the reader understand .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Have all the information","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"he or she needs","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to think about what to make of this thing . \"","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"The executive editor also defended the paper ' s more proactive approach","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"to reporting on the sexual-assault allegations against then-Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"the standard for such reporting is \" very subjective . \"","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"\" It was a live , ongoing story","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that had become the biggest political story in the country .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"It was just a different news judgment moment , \"","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Baquet said of the news cycle during Kavanaugh ' s confirmation hearings .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":81,"right":158,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":81,"left":0,"right":1,"relat